@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave
@employeeId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002

# Setelah Direct Create berhasil, copy ID dari response lalu paste di sini
@rejectActiveLeaveRequestId = 3ad93df2-841e-4784-9f0a-4678970a6fea


### ======================================================
### 1. DIRECT CREATE ACTIVE FOR REJECT TEST
### ======================================================

### Direct Create Active Leave Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic employee@company.com:123456

{
  "RequestNumber": "REQ-REJECT-001",
  "Reason": "Emergency leave using direct reject flow",
  "Employee_ID": "{{employeeId}}",
  "Status": "Drafted",
  "RequestDate": "2026-05-05T09:00:00Z"
}


### ======================================================
### 2. READ CREATED ACTIVE
### ======================================================
### Paste ID dari response Direct Create ke @rejectActiveLeaveRequestId dulu

### Read Active Leave Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{rejectActiveLeaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)


### ======================================================
### 3. SUBMIT ACTIVE LEAVE REQUEST
### ======================================================

### Submit Leave Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{rejectActiveLeaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic employee@company.com:123456

{}


### Read Submitted Leave Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{rejectActiveLeaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)


### ======================================================
### 4. REJECT SUBMITTED LEAVE REQUEST
### ======================================================

### Reject Leave Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{rejectActiveLeaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic manager@company.com:123456

{
  "Comments": "Rejected using direct create active flow test"
}


### ======================================================
### 5. READ AFTER REJECT
### ======================================================
### Saat reject masih dummy, status DB kemungkinan masih Submitted.
### Setelah reject-leave.js real, status harus berubah jadi Rejected.

### Read Rejected Leave Request with History
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{rejectActiveLeaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals